#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Shutting down Tails\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Apagar Tails\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "There are several ways of shutting down Tails:"
msgstr "Hi ha diverses maneres d'apagar Tails:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"By clicking on the system menu located in the upper right corner of the "
"screen and choosing either:"
msgstr ""
"Fent clic al menú del sistema situat a la cantonada superior dreta de la "
"pantalla i escollint:"

#. type: Bullet: '  * '
msgid ""
"[[!img lib/system-shutdown.png link=\"no\" class=\"symbolic\" alt=\"Shutdown "
"icon\"]] to shutdown the computer or"
msgstr ""
"[[!img lib/system-shutdown.png link=\"no\" class=\"symbolic\" alt=\"icona "
"d'apagar\"]] per apagar l'ordinador o"

#. type: Bullet: '  * '
msgid ""
"[[!img lib/view-refresh.png link=\"no\" class=\"symbolic\" alt=\"Restart "
"icon\"]] to restart the computer."
msgstr ""
"[[!img lib/view-refresh.png link=\"no\" class=\"symbolic\" alt=\"icona de "
"reiniciar\"]] per reiniciar l'ordinador."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  [[!img desktop/system.png link=\"no\"]]\n"
msgstr "  [[!img desktop/system.png link=\"no\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- By physically removing the USB stick or DVD that Tails is running from."
msgstr ""
"- Traient físicament el llapis USB o el DVD des del qual s'està executant "
"Tails."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  <div class=\"caution\">\n"
msgstr "  <div class=\"caution\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  <p>Only physically remove the USB stick in case of emergency as doing\n"
"  so can sometimes break the file system of the Persistent Storage.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"  <p>Traieu físicament el llapis USB només en cas d'emergència ja que\n"
"  de vegades pot trencar el sistema de fitxers de l'Emmagatzematge Persistent.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  <p>If you cannot unlock the Persistent Storage anymore after\n"
"  physically removing the USB stick, try to do a [[file system check on\n"
"  the Persistent Storage|persistent_storage/check]]\n"
"  to fix it.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"  <p>Si després d'eliminar físicament el llapis USB ja no podeu desbloquejar\n"
"  l'Emmagatzematge Persistent, proveu de fer una [[comprovació del sistema de fitxers\n"
"  de l'Emmagatzematge Persistent|persistent_storage/check]]\n"
"  per solucionar-ho.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  </div>\n"
msgstr "  </div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"When you shut down Tails, all the data stored in [[!wikipedia\n"
"Random-access_memory desc=\"RAM\"]] is erased\n"
"to protect you from [[cold boot\n"
"attacks|doc/advanced_topics/cold_boot_attacks]].\n"
msgstr ""
"Quan tanqueu Tails, totes les dades emmagatzemades a la memòria [[!wikipedia\n"
"Random-access_memory desc=\"RAM\"]] s'esborren\n"
"per protegir-vos d'[[atacs d'arrencada\n"
"en fred|doc/advanced_topics/cold_boot_attacks]].\n"
